{"tid":2051530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁錦祥：從「建設民主中國」到「香港獨立」","createTime":"2020-06-05T00:39:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T04:13:52.000Z","uid":28114,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b48e1ac9a88cc6f9ae8d4c5f7d5d219423afb8cb","tid":2051530,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T00:39:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://maddog.myradio.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/101200972_558807578161068_6264604246717497344_n-1024x682.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaddog.myradio.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2F101200972_558807578161068_6264604246717497344_n-1024x682.jpg&h=be99c789&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n子曰：「三十而立」。港人紀念六四事件的維園燭光晚會進入第三十一年，的確應該「三十而立」。「立」是甚麼意思，國學專家不同解釋，我強作解人，理解為：思想成熟，不再依附別人，有獨立批判能力，以至人格獨立。昨晚維園燭光晚會出現了革命性改變。受限聚令限制，維園少了十萬點點燭光，但參加集會的年輕人叫喊了：「香港獨立，唯一出路」口號。身為新聞工作者，在二零一四年前，我每年六四例必前往維園燭光晚會大台前排記者席作報道，很早得出結論，晚會只是行禮如儀的機械活動，叫喊了三十年的「建設民主中國」口號，但從沒有人真正探究過，若有此一日，應該行甚麼政治體制，例如：邦聯、聯邦，抑或中央集權。在二零二零年以前的維園燭光晚會，本質上只是主辦單位為選票、捐款而舉行的籌旗晚會。<br />\n<br />\n大台喊「建設民主中國」，台下很少和應，而是喊「香港獨立，誰一出路」；大台唱「自由花」，台下唱「願榮光歸香港」。若在以前，主辦單位，特別是司徒華年代，必定指有人騎劫晚會，但時移世易，以往的晚會中堅分子今年避席，冒著非法集會和違反限聚令風險出席的年輕人很清楚自己的AGENDA，主辦單位基於種種原因不敢割蓆。從政治理論角度看，「建設民主中國」與「香港獨立」兩個口號並無必然矛盾，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">現代民主必然涵括言論自由，能夠容許討論「獨立」議題的制度才算稱得上「民主」。</span>因此，六四燭光晚會本來就不應視叫喊「獨立」口號者為異端。<br />\n<br />\n從現實政治角度看，一黨專制（無論是甚麽黨）結朿之日，必定是被壓逼的少數民族爭取獨立之時。蘇共倒台，加盟共和國紛紛脱離正是先例。今天飽受打壓的藏族、維吾爾族等若有言論自由，很難想像不會要求獨立。燭光晚會主辦單位不會幼稚到以為他們會接受「高度自治」的騙局吧。<span style=\"color: red;\">現在的政治打壓愈殘酷，將來的獨立呼聲愈高昂。</span>"},{"pid":"e6ef0dd76be8325ca70da1fed4459de9bec548b3","tid":2051530,"uid":28114,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T00:40:35.000Z","msg":"國際社會會怎樣看「獨立」這個議題？現實主義者當然會説，大國重利輕義，有誰會真的理會別國人權狀況，甚至支持民族自決。不過，地緣政治板塊移動，美中關係不斷惡化，很多意想不到的事情今天都發生了。華府親臺，算不算支持「臺獨」？當勞侵（Donald Trump）和美國國會又豈會忘記北京對少數民族問題特別敏感，在適當時候刺激一下北京。執筆之際，美國國務卿龐比奧（Mike Pompeo）又再出招，聽説是制裁中國企業。美中熱戰差不多到達臨界點。<br />\n<br />\n主辦單位空談三十一年的「建設民主中國」，今天倒是有人嘗試去做。奇在此人不是王丹之流的海外民運人士，而是過氣足球名將郝海東。他和妻子前世界羽毛球冠軍葉釗穎昨日出席了爆（流料）王郭文貴的網上直播，支持「新中國聯邦」成立，並且力數中國惡行。當然，無論是郭文貴抑或是郝海東都不足以成事，但「聯邦」一詞起碼觸及「民主中國」的核心問題，是要「中央政府」，還是「聯邦政府」，邦與邦之間的關係如何&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n燭光晚會主辦單位説過「薪火相傳」，但沒有真正實行過。但<span style=\"color: red;\">時代改變了，你不肯交捧，追不上時代之輪，年輕人就燃起火炬，自行前進。</span><br />\n<br />\n梁錦祥<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://maddog.myradio.hk/2020/06/05/editor/從「建設民主中國」到「香港獨立」/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaddog.myradio.hk%2F2020%2F06%2F05%2Feditor%2F%E5%BE%9E%E3%80%8C%E5%BB%BA%E8%A8%AD%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E3%80%8D%E5%88%B0%E3%80%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E3%80%8D%2F&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EpbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=3c87b800\" target=\"_blank\">https://maddog.myradio.hk/2020/06/05/editor/從「建設民主中國」到「香港獨立」/</a>"},{"pid":"53419bab3322275985f59bb51d327214f3d67496","tid":2051530,"uid":28743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T00:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91c38ed62f40f9ca07b296ac2dc0384245acd15","tid":2051530,"uid":174639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T00:47:56.000Z","msg":"中共末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c9af0ee1174f93f7133e448321f4259c0d45a84","tid":2051530,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T00:56:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e663496c6febc4be8a008738aad48f90799db6bc","tid":2051530,"uid":31215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T01:00:52.000Z","msg":"香港突破左魔咒<br />\n就要硬撼國安法<br />\n真係多災多難<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca7f08242d5481a09041fc0fa337c122eaaa702","tid":2051530,"uid":124636,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e663496c6febc4be8a008738aad48f90799db6bc","tid":2051530,"uid":31215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T01:00:52.000Z","msg":"香港突破左魔咒<br />\n就要硬撼國安法<br />\n真係多災多難<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T01:06:30.000Z","msg":"又如何，只要個心有依個信念，等待時機利我，我地目標必成"},{"pid":"5388efab8bf977583749b6222c8d81d88ef7e8b2","tid":2051530,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T01:24:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda130b9fe6c988d0e33a391bda51713fa2cad67","tid":2051530,"uid":146030,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T01:26:11.000Z","msg":"台長好波"},{"pid":"0434ba203a2f753c8953e0a6a9200c4be060e67e","tid":2051530,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T02:12:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb40d8133bb85cc80943fddb6d7ff42bf8997c8c","tid":2051530,"uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T02:22:23.000Z","msg":"講左咁多年薪火相傳<br />\n估唔到最後係咁樣交捧<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"811f312261d82efa52b5ea18da9558012e0d7d05","tid":2051530,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fb40d8133bb85cc80943fddb6d7ff42bf8997c8c","tid":2051530,"uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T02:22:23.000Z","msg":"講左咁多年薪火相傳<br />\n估唔到最後係咁樣交捧<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T02:24:45.000Z","msg":"我哋夠估唔到陳同佳戴綠帽可以引發世界大戰喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b92048fbc6f71e6b5d329b74ccfb969540456d","tid":2051530,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T02:26:45.000Z","msg":"所羅門已收到今晚旺角便衣狗煽動人示威條片<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2051189\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2051189</a>"},{"pid":"39f064194cfcf28d3e720f5b589b305867f7dee2","tid":2051530,"uid":261913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T02:29:57.000Z","msg":"仲要多謝港獨之父689 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa76552465c6a428aa936612c39306b2f19377ec","tid":2051530,"uid":71564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T04:13:52.000Z","msg":"承先賢之志 燃革命之火<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班舊電池係時候拎去回收啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}